    {
      "id": "PopularPost376344",
      "post_content": "Like all [Act of Treason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason) effects, it can be used to steal Inspired triggers. I won a game by stealing a [King Macar, the Gold-Cursed](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=King Macar, the Gold-Cursed) with it and using his inspired trigger to exile my opponent's last blocker.  \n  \nAlso, I say [Act of Treason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason) effect instead of the more common [Threaten](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Threaten) effect because [Threaten](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Threaten) can't do this. With [Threaten](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Threaten), the creature untaps before you gain control of it, giving your opponent the inspired trigger.",
      "posted_by": "EyeballFrog",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost376344\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Like all <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Act of Treason\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason\">Act of Treason</a> effects, it can be used to steal Inspired triggers. I won a game by stealing a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"King Macar, the Gold-Cursed\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=King Macar, the Gold-Cursed\">King Macar, the Gold-Cursed</a> with it and using his inspired trigger to exile my opponent's last blocker.<br/><br/>Also, I say <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Act of Treason\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason\">Act of Treason</a> effect instead of the more common <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Threaten\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Threaten\">Threaten</a> effect because <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Threaten\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Threaten\">Threaten</a> can't do this. With <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Threaten\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Threaten\">Threaten</a>, the creature untaps before you gain control of it, giving your opponent the inspired trigger.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '376344'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy80118\">EyeballFrog</span>\r\n                                (5/17/2014 4:11:41 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
